# ================================================================
# NEXUS.ROOT.FILE
# PURPOSE:
#   EDU-style root file for NEXUS Version 3.
#   This file defines the canonical entrypoint for all NEXUS
#   operations when interacting with AVIS Version 3.

# ACTIVE VERSION:
#   NEXUS / VERSION 3

# VERSION DIRECTORY:
#   ./NEXUS/version 3/

# REQUIRED COMPONENTS:
#   NEXUS.VERSION.FILE
#   NEXUS.MANIFEST
#   NEXUS.INIT
#   AVIS.ROOT.V3
#   AVIS.EDU.FILE (from VERSION 3)

# ROBOT DIRECTIVE:
#   1. Load NEXUS.VERSION.FILE
#   2. Load NEXUS.MANIFEST
#   3. Execute NEXUS.INIT
#   4. Use AVIS.ROOT.V3 as the compatibility layer
#   5. Treat all AVIS Version 3 files as canonical input

# NOTE:
#   This file is the top-level EDU anchor for NEXUS.
# ================================================================
